latestPosts.caption:
Nidhi & Akhil - The Sneak Peek feat The Missing of the Buses 
.
.
We wanted to give a unique sneak-peek to Nidhi and Akhil that encompasses how they first met and proposed through Akhil's narration of the cute Bus Story. When they first told us the story during our Knowing the Client meeting itself, we were intrigued so wanted that part of the film. 
.
Here is the beautiful story
.
.
Shot for the cuties @nidhisudarshan and @akhilar0409 
Gorgeous Makeover @laxmilingaraju_makeupartist 
Magical Venue @thepeacockgrove 
.
.
#theeraulaaweddings #bangalorewedding #weddingteaser #theeraulaasneakpeek #sneakpeek #weddingfilm #createwithsony

Nidhi & Akhil - The Memories 
.
.
Nidhi contacted us on Gmail and we immediately connected. This was followed by our original process of sending the Know Our Clients Form. From the form, we met on a Video Call and it was an instant connection. Anupam from Peacock Grove has referred us to this amazing couple and we extend our heartfelt thanks to him. 
.
And within 6 days, Nidhi & Akhil were part of our lovely Theera Ulaa family. 
.
The wedding happened at our prestigious Peacock Grove. We had shot more than 30 weddings in this beautiful venue but every time we come there, there is something unique about the place and every photo will stand out, way different from the previous set. Amazing Anupam. 
.
.
The wedding was an intimate affair but had an amazing vibe with pomp and flair to it. Here are the beautiful memories
.
